X_n \overset{p}{\longrightarrow}\mu
\begin{align} P[|X_n-\mu|<\epsilon] &= P[-\epsilon<X_n-\mu<\epsilon] \\ &= P[-\frac{\epsilon\sqrt n}{\sigma} <\frac{\sqrt n(X_n-\mu)}{\sigma}<\frac{\epsilon\sqrt n}{\sigma}] \\ &= 2 \Phi(\frac{\epsilon\sqrt n}{\sigma})-1  \to 1 ~ as ~n \to \infty\end{align}
